7 Aham ca sarvajñasya sāgaram abhimukho ’bhavam;
8 avocatam: "Etad bruvan kim āha? kim ca
9 anyo ’yam agniḥ pratipadyate? ke caite yasya kartāraḥ?"

34 Aham ca tasmai: "Yadi aham āgamiṣyāmi, na sthāsyāmi;
35 kim punar asi tvam, yaḥ evam kṣīṇadarśanaḥ abhūḥ?"
36 Sa uvāca: "Paśya, aham ekaḥ asmīti yaḥ roditum icchāmi."

37 Aham ca tasmai: "Rudanena ca śokena ca,
38 he pāpa-ātman, tiṣṭha;
39 aham hi tvām jānāmi, yadyapi sarvataḥ mala-ākulaḥ asi."

43 Tataḥ sa bāhubhyām mama grīvāṃ paryāvartayat;
44 mama vaktram चुम्बितवान् (cumbitavān) ca āha: "He durātman,
45 sā strī dhanyā yasya garbhe tvam jātaḥ asi!

46 Saḥ puruṣaḥ loke abhimānī āsīt;
47 na asti sādhutā yasya smṛtiṃ vibhūṣayet:
48 evam asya chāyā ihātivyākulā asti.

61 Sarve akrośan: "Philipo Argenti!";
62 ca Fiorentinaḥ ātmā ugraḥ
63 ātmani eva āvartata dantaiḥ.

64 Tatrāsmān tyaktvā tam, adhikaṃ na vakṣyāmi;
65 śrotreṣu tu mama duḥkhaṃ prāharat,
66 yena aham agre cakṣuṣā dṛṣṭim vivṛtya sthitaḥ.

100 mā māṃ parityakṣīḥ," ity abraviṣam, "evam vināśitam;
101 yadi ca asmābhiḥ aparam gantum niṣidhyate,
102 asmākam padāṅkitāni punar āgacchāvaḥ kṣipram."

112 Saḥ teṣāṃ na śaknoti vaktuṃ yat teṣāṃ prāptam āsīt;
113 Aham tu tatra teṣāṃ sārdhaṃ na sthitaḥ bahu kālam,
114 Yataḥ ekaikaḥ svakīyaṃ parīkṣāṃ prati adhāvat.

124 Etāṃ teṣāṃ tracotanāṃ na navā;
125 yataḥ pūrvaṃ sā mayā upayuktā āsīt guhyadvāre,
126 yaḥ adhunāpi serrame vinā asti.
